This directory contains a base course for absolute perl and programming
beginners.

You need to know how to open a file (you already fulfill this requirement,
because otherwise you won't read this file) and you should know that F5 is
a dedicated key on your keyboard and no air force jet.

A word to the experts which might reading this:
This course should help newbies. It explains many things in an easy way and
often don't fully explain a command or gives limitations which make learning
easier but may be broken by masters who know what they're doing.
